  "title": "Account Executive (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- Handle full sets of accounts</p><p>- Prepare and submit GST return quarterly</p><p>- Prepare monthly/ quarterly financial reports and accounts schedules</p><p>- Maintaining accurate journal entries and monthly reconciliation</p><p>- Liaise with external auditors to coordinate the company’s financial year end audit</p><p>- Maintain good documentation and filing system</p><p>- Liaise with bankers when necessary</p><p>- CPF Submission</p><p>- Other Adhoc Work related to Account</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Words</p><p>- Able to work independently</p><p>- Good organization, time management and communication skills</p><p>- Experienced in ABSS accounting software</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><p>- Minimum 2 years of relevant experience in accounting<br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours </strong><br />- Report to Office 2 days a week (Monday - Friday, 9am to 6pm) </p>",
